SUMMARY:Square Dance at the Firebay
DESCRIPTION:Friday\, April 3\, 7:30-9:30 PM\, Lotus Firebay\, doors open at 7 PM.\n105 S Rogers\nAll dances will be taught. Absolutely no experience necessary. Come with or without a partner. Caller is Lotus’ own Tamara Loewenthal. Band is Donny Bradley\, Ella Jordan\, Rob McCormac\, Jack Laskey. \nCost is $5-$10\, sliding scale\nBuy Tickets for the Event
