SUMMARY:Exodus Refugee Presents: Refugee 101 at Lotus
DESCRIPTION:Date: April 21st\nTime: 6 to 7pm\nLocation: Lotus Firebay 105 S. Rogers\n\nMark Your Calendars\nOn Tuesday\, April 21st at 6 p.m.\, Exodus Refugee Immigration is partnering with Lotus to offer a “Refugee 101” presentation! Come and learn about a brief overview of refugee resettlement in the U.S.\, the work that Exodus does\, and the impacts that have been felt under the current administration. This is a casual event\, open to all\, that will offer time after the presentation and for Q&A.
URL:https://www.lotusfest.org/event/exodus-refugee-presents-refugee-101-at-lotus/
LOCATION:Lotus Firebay\, 105 S Rogers Street\, Bloomington\, IN\, 47404\, United States
CATEGORIES:Lotus Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.lotusfest.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/R101-at-Lotus-FB-event-graphic.webp
END:VEVENT
